title: Nude images and sex tape of WWE star Paige stolen and leaked online - Metro
text:
Nicole Morley for Metro.co.uk Saturday 18 Mar 2017 5:02 pm WWE Diva Paige’s nude pictures and sex tape were leaked online (Picture: Getty/WireImage) 
Private nude images and a sex tape featuring a WWE star have been leaked online. 
Paige, whose real name is Saraya-Jade Bevis, has fallen victim to hackers who’ve stolen her private pictures and posted them online without her consent. 
The wrestler, 24, confirmed the theft to her followers on Twitter. 
She said: ‘Personal and private photos of mine were stolen and unfortunately they were shared without my consent.’ 
Paige’s mother Saraya Knight supported her daughter. She said: ‘People get hacked. 
‘Unfortunately my daughter had pics and video shared from years ago. Personal and private photos of mine were stolen and unfortunately they were shared publicly without my consent. WWE Diva Paige has been out of action due to a neck injury (Picture: Getty) 
‘My husband and I support her 100%, no fault of her own.’ 
Paige is a two-time Divas Champion and was the inaugural NXT Women’s Champion in WWE’s developmental branch. 
She was the first woman to hold two titles at the same time in WWE’s history. 
Paige has been out of action for months after a nasty neck injury in October. 
She has been wrestling since she was a child, though she started appearing on the main WWE rosta in 2014. More
